// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1362 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 74380f31-1149-5d55-b57f-23722b9f0302

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
